<h1>String Theory Reading Group I</h1>

<h2>January - April '15</h2>

<p>The material discussed will roughly revolve around material presented in Polchinski: bosonic strings, conformal field theory, loop amplitudes, D\( p \)-branes etc.</p>

<p>Each meeting will go on for an hour and a half. We meet (almost) every Thursday at 6:00 PM in Hall 123.</p>


